    public class BingImageDataset<IMAGE extends Image<?,IMAGE>>
extends ReadableListDataset<IMAGE,InputStream>
implements Identifiable
    Image datasets dynamically created from the Bing search API.
    WARNING
    Some of the images inside this dataset may be set to nullif they could not be loaded.
    Author:
    Jonathon Hare (jsh2@ecs.soton.ac.uk)
